title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant
description:
In this addon spotlight I will show you several addons which are available in the area of Chernobyl including the Nuclear Power Plant known from the disaster which occurred in 1986. 

If you like to use the mod used in this video and also want to give them a try yourself? You can find the download link below:

Chernobyl NPP and Pripyat town
https://flightsim.to/file/5989/chornobyl-npp-and-pripyat-town

In addition to this both a Bush trip and a VFR flight are available:

Chernobyl Bush Trip:
https://flightsim.to/file/4210/chernobyl-bush-trip

Chernobyl Power Plant Disaster Flight Plan:
https://flightsim.to/file/14251/chernobyl-power-plant-disaster-flight-plan
